comments: Payton II (GSW) brushes Jackson's (DET) arm after he has released his jump shot attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Looney (GSW) and Bey (DET) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Poole (GSW) drives into Cunningham's (DET) chest and marginal body contact occurs as he loses control of the ball.
Poole (GSW) moves forward into Cunningham's (DET) body and delivers contact that affects his ability to secure the loose ball.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) is already in Bey's (DET) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bey (DET) and Wiggins (GSW) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Bey (DET) applies a stayed forearm to Wiggins' (GSW) body and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Bey (DET) is moving alongside Wiggins' (GSW) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Bey (DET) brings his left hand up and makes contact with Wiggins' (GSW) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Cunningham (DET) briefly grasps and releases Payton II's (GSW) jersey and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Grant (DET) is already in Payton II's (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) is moving alongside Bey's (DET) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Payton II (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Bey's (DET) shot near the rim.
Bey (DET) touches the ball while it is inside the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Looney (GSW) makes contact with Grant's (DET) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Cunningham (DET) and Wiggins (GSW) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Wiggins secures the ball.
Cunningham (DET) jumps to the side of Wiggins (GSW) and cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) is moving alongside Grant's (DET) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Joseph (DET) cleanly deflects the ball away from Wiggins (GSW) during rebounding.  Any ensuing arm contact after the deflection is considered incidental.
Payton II (GSW) jumps to the side of Jackson (DET) and avoids making contact with Jackson during his jump shot attempt.
